# Captcha images live in a private GitHub repo and are fetched at build
# time by scripts/fetch-captcha-images.ts. Keeping them out of the public
# repo prevents a cloner from building a perceptual-hash cheat table.
# The generated json manifest embeds the same binaries and is likewise kept
# out of the public repo.
/lib/captcha/images/*.jpg
/lib/captcha/_images.generated.json
